{
  "stem": "3631.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You buy the material, you design it, you make it, you put it on the train tonight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was quite a difficult decision to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "First of all, we had never done this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my father did it with-- with-- with tears in his eyes, but it was done.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's an experience we did not--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] ?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What year?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Must have been 1936 or 1937.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were thrown out of Germany, my father's sister, who-- who lived in Cologne, was visiting with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- she was staying with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they took us away, they-- they kept her there, and she closed everything up, and that-- that was it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was young, and as a young fellow, you-- you don't take it that seriously.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could not go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Came a point where we could go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could not go to a theater.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We could not go swimming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could go swim in the river, but not-- not in a-- in a bath, in a public bath.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I joined a small social club.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It got together once-- once in a-- once a month, just talking about different things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all these club meetings had to be reported to the-- to the Gestapo, and for every club meeting, a civilian SS man or [INAUDIBLE] was present there to-- to see what we had to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you were not free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You just were not free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were other things that didn't personally affect me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were a lot of arrests, and disappearances, and the first words about concentration camps became known.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- but these were, at this point, still once removed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I do not remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
